<p>Arvut is a socio-educational network established with the aim to lead a grassroots shift in Israeli society and in the Jewish population around the world; a shift towards healthier, more balanced societies, achieving sustainable, shared happiness.</p>
<p>We are a non profit organization registered in Israel.</p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Our Goal</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr">The goal of The Arvut network is to improve the quality of life in our communities and the society we live in by uplifting the values of mutual guarantee and collaboration. The notion of mutual guarantee, which was fostered and cultivated for centuries by the Jewish people, holds within it the awareness that our personal well-being and the well-being of society are interdependent. We aim to restore that notion and embed it into our daily lives to improve all functions of our society.</p>
