<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Round Table Events</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr">Round Table events are held in different venues, from city squares, to university halls and business organizations.The Round Table platform is used to provide the conditions for fruitful multilateral discussions which bring people of different backgrounds to solve their problems together. Such experiences of successful collaboration through the connection of hearts and minds, create a culture of productive, connective discourse, essential to any community, group or organization. At the Round Table all participants express their opinion equally. The discussions are guided by a moderator who raises a wide range of questions, relevant to the shared goals of the participants. Previous Round Table events have successfully brought together employees and managers, social activists, representatives of public organizations and the media, as well as experts in different fields. The results have been new found solutions to difficult problems, a sense of trust, joy and cooperation that fostered hope and positive initiatives.</p>
